headline.main: Rain Washes Out Final of Brazil Open
headline.print_headline: Rain Washes Out Final of Brazil Open

lead_paragraph: Rain has washed out the final of the clay-court Brazil Open with Pablo Cuevas of Uruguay trying for this third straight title in the tournament as he faces Albert Ramos-Vinolas of Spain.
